des: We all want to do good - whether it’s for our family, friends, the planet, or society at large. No matter how big or small, good deeds carry a positive impact to all those around us and ripple outward. Alexa is here to help you improve the lives of others and positively change the world. Simply say: Alexa, launch Daily Good!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
